      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Proof of Courage",
        "Client": "Admiral Galleus",
        "Description": "You are to descend the\r\ncrater, locate Gaismagorm,\r\nand then defeat it. The fate\r\nof the Kingdom... Kamura...\r\nThe fate of us all depends upon\r\nyour success. Go forth, Hero\r\nof Kamura, and be victorious!",
        "Target": "Slay Gaismagorm",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Preuve de bravoure",
        "Client": "Amiral Galleus",
        "Description": "Tu vas devoir descendre dans\r\nle crat\u00E8re, rep\u00E9rer le Gaismagorm,\r\net le vaincre. Le sort de tout\r\nle Royaume repose sur toi.\r\nNous t\u0027aiderons dans cette\r\nqu\u00EAte, l\u00E9gende de Kamura !",
        "Target": "Tuer le Gaismagorm",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Prova di coraggio",
        "Client": "Ammiraglio Galleus",
        "Description": "Devi scendere nel cratere,\r\nindividuare il Gaismagorm\r\ne sconfiggerlo. L\u0027esito non\r\ndeterminer\u00E0 solo il fato del\r\nregno, ma anche quello dei\r\nnostri vicini. Verremo con te\r\nin questa missione, Audace!",
        "Target": "Uccidi il Gaismagorm",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Mut unter Beweis gestellt",
        "Client": "Galleus",
        "Description": "Steige den Krater hinab, finde\r\nden Gaismagorm und besiege\r\nihn. Das Schicksal des K\u00F6nig-\r\nreichs... von Kamura... Das\r\nSchicksal aller h\u00E4ngt von deinem\r\nErfolg ab. Geh voran, \u003CLSNR {Held} {Heldin}\u003E\r\nvon Kamura, und sei siegreich!",
        "Target": "Erlege den Gaismagorm.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Una prueba de osad\u00EDa",
        "Client": "Almirante Galleus",
        "Description": "Queremos que bajes al cr\u00E1ter,\r\nque localices a Gaismagorm y\r\nque lo derrotes. La suerte del\r\nreino, de Kamura... y de todos\r\nnosotros depende de tu \u00E9xito.\r\n\u00A1Ve, \u003CLSNR {h\u00E9roe} {hero\u00EDna}\u003E de Kamura,\r\ny \u00E1lzate con la victoria!",
        "Target": "Abate a Gaismagorm",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041F\u0440\u0438\u043C\u0435\u0440 \u0445\u0440\u0430\u0431\u0440\u043E\u0441\u0442\u0438",
